flowRoot.flowPara: Hello. My name is Wessel Stoop. I work with language & machine learning, and make videogames in my free time. This website aims to be a complete collection of (1) the texts I write, (2) what I produce academically, (3) the games I create (4) any other stuff I program (like websites) and (5) what the media write about all of the above. Furthermore, this website contains some pictures of me to prove that I totally do not all of my days staring at a computer screen.
